content: My name is Jac, and my Chinese name is Tang-Jie Chang (張堂傑). I am studying Master Degree in computer science at National Chiao Tung University and supervised by Prof. Yung-Ju (Stanley) Chang. Now my research is on helping user guess the notification’s source. I also started to get interested in UX research and front-end web design in later semester of my 1st grade master.
